name: dolichyl-phosphate beta-D-mannosyltransferase
reaction: GDP-alpha-D-mannose + dolichyl phosphate = GDP + dolichyl beta-D-mannosyl phosphate [RN:R01009]
comment: Acts only on long-chain polyprenyl phosphates and alpha-dihydropolyprenyl phosphates that are larger than C35.
